title: BREASTFEEDING...let's chat about it! | EP 43
itunes:author: Yeah No I Know, Jenna, Brooklin & Kristen Leanne
description:
Breastfeeding vs. Formula.

The joys and the difficulties of breastfeeding! And not everyone can bf?!

Are you comfortable breastfeeding in public? Has the formula shortage affected you?


Today is all things about feeding a baby! If you have a baby or want one some day, these are some of the things we learned along our journeys and wish we knew before hand!


We know we have some mommas on here so please share your experiences and any tips you have for others! We are all in this together!



We are also on Spotify, Apple Podcast and more! Search "Yeah No I Know".

* Everything we talk about on this podcast is our own individual opinions, not fact. Research everything for yourself and make the best decisions for you.
